。截至2018年12月31日，BCT 集團股東的總資產值及股本總額已分別超逾港幣 22,615億及港幣2,921億。現時，BCT 銀聯集團的特定銀行網絡合共擁有310多間分行。</code>"},{"pid":"352763d9485b0c3380430b5c64f58c5fc2ffcb1b","tid":1637954,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T09:00:27.000Z","msg":"呢個係銀聯<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2qpRsuE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2qpRsuE.png&h=c7560847&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個係銀聯BCT<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GB49YBr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGB49YBr.png&h=ce9ead1b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c70310d4dc6be9512ca549aef66a500a513f28cc","tid":1637954,"uid":77717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"352763d9485b0c3380430b5c64f58c5fc2ffcb1b","tid":1637954,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T09:00:27.000Z","msg":"呢個係銀聯<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2qpRsuE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2qpRsuE.png&h=c7560847&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個係銀聯BCT<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GB49YBr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGB49YBr.png&h=ce9ead1b&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T09:07:40.000Z","msg":"多謝提醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1077ca4a4c71d9cbf3781f93e98d424184d88e87","tid":1637954,"uid":1082,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c70310d4dc6be9512ca549aef66a500a513f28cc","tid":1637954,"uid":77717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"352763d9485b0c3380430b5c64f58c5fc2ffcb1b","tid":1637954,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T09:00:27.000Z","msg":"呢個係銀聯<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2qpRsuE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2qpRsuE.png&h=c7560847&s={SIZE}\" /><